    {
      "id": "4f539428-fdab-421a-8a72-63297967d530",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Prediction of student performance is one the most relevant tasks in LA. However, traditional methods are designed for balanced datasets which is somewhat difficult in datasets intended to detect students at-risk. To address the imabalance, the authors propose a framework that combines an auto-encoder with a Deep NN. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "4f539428-fdab-421a-8a72-63297967d530",
        "parent": {
          "type": "page_id",
