    {
      "id": "a5ea1c95-a039-48fd-9254-a6b98844a546",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The auto-encoder is intended to generate new instances of students at-risk first, the neural network is meant to make predictions. Experiments of performed on benchmark dataset show that the model actually is a possible alternative to generate samples that make the datasets more balanced. Confirmation tests validate effectiveness and robustness of the designed approach.  ",
